<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/54601APCBTLTSHPQHKCBSVQKSMGPHQNNB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Father's Day Matinee";
  schema:description """
	This Father’s Day, head down to The Improv Centre to celebrate Fathers and father-figures-alike, with an afternoon of laughter! Dedicated towards backyard ball games, bad puns and all things we love most about our role-models, this delightfully dad-inspired show will be fun for the whole family!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: PG <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is a Special Show – Restricted vouchers and TIX do not apply
""";
