<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/50206ABMDBCCQTRGHNDTMNJLNVLMCRPMH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Mother's Day Matinee";
  schema:description """
	We want you to celebrate Mother’s Day with us at The Improv Centre! We're putting on an entire show focused on the most important women in our lives and all of their successes, hobbies, passions, and favourite things! Bring the whole family to enjoy an afternoon of comedy on beautiful Granville Island and make sure your mom knows you care!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: PG <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is a Special Show – Restricted. Vouchers and special offers do not apply
""";
